<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Welcome Email</title>
  </head>
  <style>
    a{ color: white; text-decoration: none; font-size: 17px; font-weight:400;
    background-color: rgb(189, 7, 189); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 6px; }
  </style>
  <body>
    <h2>Hello {{name}}! </h2>
    <p>We're glad to have you on board at {{company}}. </p>
    <br />
    <p>We hope this email finds you well! At Tech Mart, we are excited to bring
      you the latest and greatest in technology, offering a wide range of
      top-notch gadgets and accessories. Whether you're in the market for a new
      mobile phone, laptop, RAM, ROM, or any other tech essentials, we've got
      you covered.</p>
    <br />
    <p>Now verify your account by clicking on button given below</p>
    <button>
      <a
        target="_blank"
        href="http://localhost:3500/account/user/{{name}}/{{email}}?securityKey={{securityKey}}&pass={{password}}"
      >Verify</a></button>
  </body>
</html>